METHODOLOGY:
This bill amends the credit carryforward limits for the Business Profits Tax and Business
Enterprise Tax. Currently the credit carry forward limit is 500% with further decreases
scheduled to a 250% limit for taxable periods ending on or after December 31, 2029 and to a
100% limit for taxable periods ending on or after December 31, 2031. This bill will change the
creditcarryforwardlimitstobethefollowing:
